<h4>Motivating and inspiring others to make positive changes</h4>

<p>With a background in psychology, peak performance training and intense traditional martial arts, Edmond knows first-hand the importance of effective leadership skills, personal growth and motivation. His experience and passion within these areas come through in his seminars and consulting sessions.</p>

<p>He applies cutting-edge research and real-world applications to create strategies that address even the most challenging professional and personal obstacles – challenges we all face.
Face to face and long-distance training</p>

<p>Edmond works with clients throughout the world, including the U.S., New Zealand, and Australia. He travels to clients’ sites to deliver his team-building conferences and seminars, including “Personal Balance,” “The Secret is Resilience” and “Kick Start Forward Movement,” while most of his personal and professional development coaching is conducted long distance, by phone, Skype, or other mode of communication.</p>
